sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Student as Обучающийся
    participant Moodle as Moodle (PEP)
    participant Observer as Event Observer Plugin (PHP)
    participant API as Backend API (FastAPI)
    participant Progress as ProgressService
    participant Reasoner as ReasoningOrchestrator
    participant Cache as Redis

    Note over Student,Moodle: Студент завершает активность в Moodle
    Student->>Moodle: завершить module / quiz / assignment
    Moodle-->>Moodle: обновить course_modules_completion / quiz_attempts

    Note over Moodle,Observer: Плагин-наблюдатель ловит событие Moodle
    Moodle->>Observer: \core\event\course_module_completion_updated
    Note right of Observer: или \mod_quiz\event\attempt_submitted

    Observer->>API: POST /api/v1/events/progress
    Note right of Observer: payload: {student_id, element_id,<br/>event_type: completed|viewed,<br/>value?: float, timestamp}

    API->>Progress: register_progress(payload)
    Progress->>Progress: update_progress: запись факта в ABox
    API-->>Observer: 202 Accepted

    Note over Progress,Reasoner: Дальнейший пересчёт идёт в фоне
    Progress->>Reasoner: rerun_reasoning_and_rebuild_cache(student_id)

    Reasoner->>Cache: DEL access:{student_id}
    Reasoner->>Reasoner: полный прогон логического вывода
    Reasoner->>Cache: SET access:{student_id}

    Note over Observer,Moodle: При следующем рендере Moodle снова<br/>дёрнет проверку доступности
